621
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:13,680
We'll vote on this issue. Alright?

622
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:22,890
Okay.

623
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:25,790
I have a motion for discussion

624
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:28,650
in the meeting as well.

625
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:35,230
[A Motion to Improve the Firm's Voting System]

626
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:37,770
Let there be a vote.

627
00:28:07,860 --> 00:28:08,730
Oh no.

628
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,150
Tao Zheng is too aggressive.

629
00:28:12,250 --> 00:28:13,930
We must stop him.

630
00:28:14,520 --> 00:28:16,920
We'll have a partners' meeting right away.

631
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:18,590
I want every partner

632
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:20,580
to know what he has done.

633
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,760
Forget it.

634
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:25,790
Why?

635
00:28:26,990 --> 00:28:28,190
