636
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:32,310
Some of our partners

637
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:33,700
have always wanted to change

638
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:35,590
the voting system.

639
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:36,980
In other words,

640
00:28:37,150 --> 00:28:39,550
they want to cancel the extra vote you have.

641
00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:42,430
Now, he's only one or two votes

642
00:28:42,430 --> 00:28:44,000
short of you.

643
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,230
If we insist that he should give the case

644
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:47,190
back to the young lawyers,

645
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:50,290
he might incite others to do something

646
00:28:50,870 --> 00:28:52,800
that could end up backfiring on us.

647
00:28:55,660 --> 00:28:57,290
Look at the signatures on the motion.

648
00:28:57,290 --> 00:28:59,970
Mr. Han has gained support from many people.

649
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,930
So the extra vote in your hand

650
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:08,170
is really important to us.

651
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:14,630
It's just a case.

652
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:17,660
Those two young lawyers aren't worth so many efforts.

653
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:01,630
Tell Qiu Hua and Luo Yingzi

654
00:30:01,630 --> 00:30:02,910
to come to my office.

655
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,850
He had a huge smile.

656
00:30:08,120 --> 00:30:09,140
The situation must be bad for us.

657
00:30:09,140 --> 00:30:10,140
What should we do?

658
00:30:11,010 --> 00:30:12,540
We have no choice. Let's go.

659
00:30:13,050 --> 00:30:13,560
Wait.

660
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:15,630
If the firm chooses him,

661
00:30:15,670 --> 00:30:17,470
we won't go down without a fight.

662
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:18,400
Do you think the firm

663
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:19,780
will offend a seasoned lawyer

664
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:21,110
for us?

665
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,940
But we're on the righteous side.

666
00:30:24,230 --> 00:30:25,530
When it's about interests,

667
00:30:25,530 --> 00:30:27,250
who cares about righteousness?

668
00:30:27,250 --> 00:30:28,250
Just wait and see.

669
00:30:32,220 --> 00:30:33,150
Qiu Hua, Yingzi.

670
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:37,050
I think you two

671
00:30:37,290 --> 00:30:39,850
should move onto next case.

672
00:30:40,490 --> 00:30:41,410
As for this case,

673
00:30:41,410 --> 00:30:45,010
Mr. Han signed the contract first.

674
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:45,840
I can't change that.

675
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:46,630
Why?

676
00:30:47,630 --> 00:30:49,440
He can annul the agreement

677
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:51,380
for conflicts of interest.

678
00:30:51,610 --> 00:30:53,960
We took the case first.

679
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:57,310
But he signed the contract

680
00:30:57,660 --> 00:30:59,370
before you did, right?

681
00:31:06,890 --> 00:31:07,560
Ms. Fang,

682
00:31:08,890 --> 00:31:10,860
what happened in such a short time?

683
00:31:12,050 --> 00:31:14,450
Why did you suddenly change your attitude?

684
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,160
If people follow suit,

685
00:31:17,300 --> 00:31:18,930
and sign a contract with Party A

686
00:31:18,930 --> 00:31:21,860
when they hear someone else would represent Party B,

687
00:31:21,930 --> 00:31:24,140
there will be a huge mess.

688
00:31:25,250 --> 00:31:25,810
Ms. Fang,

689
00:31:26,190 --> 00:31:28,320
I've wanted to say this for a long time.

690
00:31:29,270 --> 00:31:31,960
Doesn't the firm know how Han Zhitong suppresses the young?

691
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,470
There are so many young people in the Criminal Defense Department.

692
00:31:33,470 --> 00:31:36,070
Only we two became attorneys at law in recent years.

693
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:38,070
He divides a case into several parts

694
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:39,540
and put young lawyers

695
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:41,170
into different groups

696
00:31:41,350 --> 00:31:43,610
so that they wouldn't have a chance to work cases alone.

697
00:31:43,610 --> 00:31:45,000
They'll have to rely on him forever.

698
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:45,870
Under such circumstances,

699
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:47,400
young people can't grow up.

700
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:51,470
Does the firm not know about this?

701
00:31:51,470 --> 00:31:53,730
Is it the firm's decision to indulge him?

702
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:57,900
He's done a really bad thing.

703
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:59,780
Is the firm still taking his side?

704
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:01,490
It's unfair.

705
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:06,950
Who are you accusing?

706
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:07,910
I'm not accusing anyone.

707
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:09,270
I'm just stating the facts.

708
00:32:09,270 --> 00:32:10,140
What facts?

709
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:12,570
When you got this case,

710
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:15,860
didn't you take your personal gains under consideration?

711
00:32:16,470 --> 00:32:18,400
Tao Zheng and Zhang Zhi have told me

712
00:32:18,410 --> 00:32:20,930
that you asked them to support you.

713
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:24,770
That's why Han Zhitong interfered with it. Do you know that?

714
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:26,190
If you had been open about

715
00:32:26,190 --> 00:32:27,980
your meeting with the client,

716
00:32:28,390 --> 00:32:30,460
and won your client's trust

717
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:32,610
with your ability and sincerity,

718
00:32:32,610 --> 00:32:34,670
you wouldn't have ended up like this.

719
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:37,510
Your plan went south,

720
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:40,020
so you thought of me.

721
00:32:43,170 --> 00:32:44,890
If you are competent lawyers,

722
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:46,870
No one can suppress you.

723
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:49,310
Stop pretending to be innocent.

724
00:32:50,270 --> 00:32:52,070
Don't you take that tone with me.

725
00:32:54,430 --> 00:32:56,670
Go and think about it before you come again.

726
00:32:56,670 --> 00:32:57,400
I'm busy.

727
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:27,430
What kind of person is he?

728
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:30,470
Sour loser!

729
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:35,320
Shame on him!

730
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:39,440
Are we gonna let him take the case away?

731
00:33:39,910 --> 00:33:41,050
What else can we do?

732
00:33:42,080 --> 00:33:44,130
Maybe we should see it as a valuable lesson.

733
00:33:44,130 --> 00:33:45,160
I don't believe it.

734
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:47,360
We're smart people. Can't we fight him?

735
00:33:48,650 --> 00:33:49,820
What else can we do?

736
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:51,600
He has taken the case.

737
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:53,500
If we contact Mr. Wei again,

738
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,900
we'll violate the rules.

739
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,640
We have no choice.

740
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,120
We can do worse things to him.

741
00:34:03,150 --> 00:34:05,260
Get a bigger villain to punish him.

742
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:15,179
Hello, Ms. Mei.

743
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:18,570
What?

744
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:20,949
Okay.

745
00:34:21,090 --> 00:34:22,270
I'll be there soon.

746
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:23,830
I'm sorry.

747
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:25,949
What's wrong?

748
00:34:25,949 --> 00:34:27,290
Did she cause you trouble again?

749
00:34:27,290 --> 00:34:28,960
It's enough that she causes me trouble,

750
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,230
but now she's even messing with Ms. Mei.

751
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,630
So annoying.

752
00:34:31,650 --> 00:34:32,710
I'll go take a look.

753
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:34,770
You think about how to fight that guy.

754
00:35:03,450 --> 00:35:04,240
Ms. Mei.

755
00:35:06,350 --> 00:35:08,240
Some people came,

756
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:10,050
including a woman.

757
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,330
They beat her up.

758
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:13,260
It was

759
00:35:14,150 --> 00:35:15,170
a huge mess.

760
00:35:15,720 --> 00:35:17,200
What do you think we should do?

761
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:20,130
Everyone knows that I recommended her to this place.

762
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:21,460
Ms. Mei.

763
00:35:21,990 --> 00:35:23,620
I got her here.

764
00:35:23,890 --> 00:35:25,290
Sorry for troubling you.

765
00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:26,960
Please don't be mad.

766
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:29,220
I shouldn't keep you here any longer.

767
00:35:29,220 --> 00:35:30,280
I'll deal with her.

768
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,160
Yingzi.

769
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:43,150
Tell me what happened.

770
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:45,880
Yingzi.

771
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,560
I didn't cause trouble.

772
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,590
Mr. Zhou's wife brought a crowd

773
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:53,150
to the school and beat me up.

774
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:55,490
Look what they did to me.

775
00:35:57,530 --> 00:35:59,460
They should've treated you worse.

776
00:36:00,740 --> 00:36:02,710
Yingzi, I've been bullied.

777
00:36:02,890 --> 00:36:04,510
How could you say that?

778
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,840
Why are you bullied?

779
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,200
Why?

780
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,510
What's the reason?

781
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:13,360
It's because of that shameless woman!

782
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:15,360
She knew Zhou Houze was with me,

783
00:36:15,390 --> 00:36:16,790
but she just wouldn't leave him.

784
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:18,670
Why would she?

785
00:36:18,810 --> 00:36:20,490
She's Mr. Zhou's legal spouse.

786
00:36:20,490 --> 00:36:21,900
They're a legitimate couple.

787
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:23,540
What are you doing now?

788
00:36:23,830 --> 00:36:25,160
You're pushing her for a divorce.

789
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:26,690
How can she not be mad at you?

790
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,260
How can she not beat you up?

791
00:36:41,310 --> 00:36:42,510
Yingzi,

792
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:45,670
you're the only one I can count on now.

793
00:36:46,180 --> 00:36:47,730
Mr. Zhou admires you.

794
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:49,260
Can you go

795
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:51,560
and persuade him to divorce his wife?

796
00:36:52,810 --> 00:36:54,730
Do you know what admiration is?

797
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:58,830
That's just a gangster's empty gesture.

798
00:36:59,170 --> 00:37:00,570
Do you really believe it?

799
00:37:00,730 --> 00:37:03,650
He would've got a divorce if he wanted to

800
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:05,140
without anyone's advice!

801
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,990
Also, Lanlan,

802
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:10,220
I can't do it.

803
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:13,000
And I don't want to tell anyone to divorce.

804
00:37:13,050 --> 00:37:14,900
What should we do now?

805
00:37:15,330 --> 00:37:17,600
Yingzi, I got to know him because of you.

806
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,800
