807
00:37:19,820 --> 00:37:20,460
I love him.

808
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:22,120
I want to be with him.

809
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:24,290
Did I tell you to date him?

810
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:32,600
It's true

811
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:36,740
that you two knew each other because of me.

812
00:37:38,330 --> 00:37:39,190
How about this?

813
00:37:40,950 --> 00:37:42,810
It's wrong for his wife to hit you.

814
00:37:42,860 --> 00:37:44,520
I'll talk about that with him.

815
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:47,800
Thank you.

816
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,820
I know you're the best!

817
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:02,810
Hello, Qiu Hua.

818
00:38:02,940 --> 00:38:04,060
Hello, Yingzi.

819
00:38:04,250 --> 00:38:05,740
Mr. Wei called me just now.

820
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,620
He didn't know what had happened.

821
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:09,940
He urged us to sign the contract with him.

822
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,470
You didn't tell him?

823
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:13,600
I couldn't explain it on the phone.

824
00:38:14,030 --> 00:38:15,510
He wants to meet us now.

825
00:38:16,070 --> 00:38:17,110
But at this time,

826
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,450
