827
00:38:18,450 --> 00:38:20,580
We'll be in trouble if Mr. Han knows it.

828
00:38:20,830 --> 00:38:21,980
I'm not afraid of him.

829
00:38:21,980 --> 00:38:23,140
I'll meet with Mr. Wei.

830
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:24,220
Yes. I thought so.

831
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:25,620
You happen to be outside.

832
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:26,670
Go see him

833
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:27,720
and explain to him.

834
00:38:27,720 --> 00:38:30,250
Maybe there will be chances for cooperation.

835
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:32,830
He's in the tea house where we met him last time.

836
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:34,000
Okay, bye.

837
00:38:47,810 --> 00:38:48,800
-Mr. Wei.
-Ms. Luo.

838
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:49,630
Mr. Wei. Mr. Wei.

839
00:38:49,630 --> 00:38:50,550
I heard from Ms. Qiu

840
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:51,550
that you would drop the case.

841
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:52,260
Why?

842
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:53,360
Mr. Wei, calm down.

843
00:38:53,390 --> 00:38:54,210
Let's sit down and talk.

