00:38:54,210 --> 00:38:55,600
Okay.

845
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:58,220
If it's about the fee,

846
00:38:58,430 --> 00:39:00,420
we can talk about it anytime.

847
00:39:00,830 --> 00:39:01,590
Alright?

848
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:03,110
Mr. Wei, here is the thing.

849
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:04,950
It's not about the fee.

850
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:07,440
Do you remember Mr. Han,

851
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,200
the man we ate with last time?

852
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:10,290
Yes.

853
00:39:10,310 --> 00:39:12,600
He went ahead of us

854
00:39:12,750 --> 00:39:15,740
and signed a representation contract with your wife.

855
00:39:15,740 --> 00:39:17,020
With my wife?

856
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:22,870
So we can't

857
00:39:22,930 --> 00:39:23,800
represent you anymore.

858
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:24,600
I understand.

859
00:39:24,610 --> 00:39:26,550
There's a conflict of interest.

860
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,710
Mr. Han

861
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:30,960
is quite immoral.

862
00:39:30,990 --> 00:39:31,630
I agree.

863
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:32,490
I didn't know people could be worse

864
00:39:32,490 --> 00:39:34,130
than imagination.

865
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,200
What should we do now?

866
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,070
We have no choice now.

867
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:41,520
A law firm can't represent the plaintiff

868
00:39:41,570 --> 00:39:44,210
and defendant at the same time.

869
00:39:44,700 --> 00:39:45,510
The point is

870
00:39:45,540 --> 00:39:47,710
where can I find other lawyers

871
00:39:47,750 --> 00:39:50,120
as good as you two?

872
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:50,800
No. Listen.

873
00:39:50,850 --> 00:39:51,670
Actually, Mr. Wei,

874
00:39:51,670 --> 00:39:53,680
there are many good lawyers.

875
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:55,410
Why don't you keep looking?

876
00:39:57,190 --> 00:39:58,070
Ms. Luo,

877
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,760
to be honest,

878
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:01,900
I only trust you and Ms. Qiu now.

879
00:40:02,410 --> 00:40:03,220
Why don't you

880
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:05,420
recommend a lawyer to me?

881
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:09,650
We don't have much experience.

882
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:10,990
In fact, in this line of business,

883
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:12,800
we only know a little number of people.

884
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:15,260
This has nothing to do with your experience.

885
00:40:15,470 --> 00:40:17,870
I'm an outsider.

886
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:18,950
I'm not familiar with the legal profession.

887
00:40:18,950 --> 00:40:20,750
You are working in this line of business.

888
00:40:20,750 --> 00:40:21,630
Personally speaking,

889
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:22,750
I know nothing

890
00:40:22,750 --> 00:40:24,080
about your line of work.

891
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,620
You've gotta help me.

892
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:27,070
I'm telling you the truth here.

893
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,660
If you don't help me,

894
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:30,510
Will you help me?

895
00:40:31,660 --> 00:40:32,290
Will you?

896
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:55,310
Ms. Luo.

897
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,460
Is your boss upstairs?

898
00:40:57,650 --> 00:40:58,600
Yes, upstairs.

899
00:40:58,630 --> 00:40:59,620
Okay, thank you.

900
00:41:00,350 --> 00:41:02,870
Just say how much you charge. It's fine.

901
00:41:03,010 --> 00:41:03,960
We are brothers.

902
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:04,840
Come in.

903
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:06,400
Just say it.

904
00:41:07,310 --> 00:41:08,310
Mr. Zhou.

905
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,640
How ungrateful you are!

906
00:41:10,640 --> 00:41:12,370
I thought you've forgotten me.

907
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:14,030
No. I just

908
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:15,910
don't want to come to this place.

909
00:41:15,910 --> 00:41:18,170
When I'm here, I feel like I owe you money.

910
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:19,760
Silly girl.

911
00:41:19,790 --> 00:41:20,940
Come on. Let me introduce you to him.

912
00:41:20,940 --> 00:41:21,850
This is Mr. Chen.

913
00:41:21,850 --> 00:41:23,380
You can stop here, Mr. Zhou.

914
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:25,070
I know she's Ms. Luo.

915
00:41:26,970 --> 00:41:29,470
It's been a few days since we last met. Have you digested the bird's nest soup yet?

916
00:41:29,470 --> 00:41:31,980
Good for you to expand your business this far.

917
00:41:31,980 --> 00:41:33,870
Now you've even taken jobs from Mr. Zhou.

918
00:41:33,870 --> 00:41:34,510
Can't I?

919
00:41:34,990 --> 00:41:37,050
I once represented Mr. Zhou in a case.

920
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,370
What a shame it was

921
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:40,000
that I wasn't part of the case

922
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,510
involving you and him!

923
00:41:41,720 --> 00:41:43,320
I didn't make money from you.

924
00:41:43,470 --> 00:41:44,330
My friends,

925
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:44,990
let's not talk about money.

926
00:41:44,990 --> 00:41:45,920
Don't talk about money.

927
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:47,720
I see her as my little sister now.

928
00:41:47,940 --> 00:41:50,060
Wait. Are you acquaintances?

929
00:41:50,200 --> 00:41:51,000
We're fellow law practitioners.

930
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,240
No.

931
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:55,090
In my previous case about loans,

932
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:57,080
he represented the bank.

933
00:41:57,140 --> 00:41:58,680
He made me homeless.

934
00:41:58,780 --> 00:42:00,190
Don't be so petty.

935
00:42:00,210 --> 00:42:01,080
Stop with the word game.

936
00:42:01,080 --> 00:42:02,340
You're a lawyer and I'm a lawyer.

937
00:42:02,340 --> 00:42:03,580
Doesn't that make us fellow law practitioners?

938
00:42:03,580 --> 00:42:06,060
I have nothing to say to you.

939
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:09,800
Mr. Zhou,

940
00:42:10,200 --> 00:42:11,380
I need to talk to you.

941
00:42:13,580 --> 00:42:14,640
Alright, Mr. Zhou.

942
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:16,570
Now you see it.

943
00:42:16,790 --> 00:42:18,340
You hear the tone she takes.

944
00:42:18,470 --> 00:42:19,900
I'd better be sensible

945
00:42:19,930 --> 00:42:20,880
and show myself out.

946
00:42:20,880 --> 00:42:21,900
I'll leave you alone.

947
00:42:21,900 --> 00:42:22,400
Are you leaving?

948
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:22,990
Yeah.

949
00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:24,880
About this,

950
00:42:25,270 --> 00:42:26,510
don't worry. It's no big deal.

951
00:42:26,510 --> 00:42:27,910
I won't walk you out then.

952
00:42:31,590 --> 00:42:32,770
The fact that you could afford a new car

953
00:42:32,770 --> 00:42:34,880
means you're able to repay your loans.

954
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,740
Don't forget to pay the bank on time.

955
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:38,420
Why are you so mean?

956
00:42:39,010 --> 00:42:40,430
You've taken my apartment away.

957
00:42:40,430 --> 00:42:41,390
What else do you want?

958
00:42:41,390 --> 00:42:42,890
Do you have a problem with me buying a car?

959
00:42:42,890 --> 00:42:43,420
No. Not at all.

960
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,340
Easy, lady.

961
00:42:44,460 --> 00:42:46,060
Just enjoy what you have now.

962
00:42:46,670 --> 00:42:47,480
I suggest you

963
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:48,190
drive your car

964
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:49,150
as much as possible.

965
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:49,870
Have fun with it.

966
00:42:49,870 --> 00:42:51,470
Maybe one day, I, an unscrupulous lawyer,

967
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,930
will take it away from you.

968
00:42:53,550 --> 00:42:54,290
Wait.

969
00:42:55,210 --> 00:42:56,270
Mr. Zhou, find him a place.

970
00:42:56,270 --> 00:42:57,670
Keep him here for a while.

971
00:42:57,730 --> 00:42:58,660
I need to talk to you.
